OL,3,CFamilies of IRA men shot dead reach
OL,4,Csettlements in claims for damages
OL,6,FThe families of two IRA men shot dead
OL,7,Fby British soldiers nearly 43 years
OL,8,Fago have reached settlements in their
OL,9,Fclaims for damages, the High Court
OL,10,Fheard today.
OL,12,FBrian Campbell, 19, and Colm McGirr,
OL,13,F23, died after the SAS mounted an
OL,14,Foperation at the scene of an arms dump
OL,15,Fnear Coalisland, Co Tyrone in December
OL,16,F1983.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
