PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778253065
OL,3,CFamilies of IRA men shot dead reach
OL,4,Csettlements in claims for damages
OL,6,FRelatives of both men sued the
OL,7,FMinistry of Defence (MoD) and the
OL,8,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,9,F(PSNI), alleging a shoot-to-kill
OL,10,Fpolicy and lack of effective
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FIn court today it was announced that
OL,14,Fboth actions have been settled on
OL,15,Fconfidential terms.
OL,17,FThe families are to make a donation to
OL,18,Fcharity following the outcome.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
