OL,3,CFamilies of IRA men shot dead reach
OL,4,Csettlements in claims for damages
OL,6,FCampbell and McGirr were shot dead
OL,7,Fafter they attended the weapons cache
OL,8,Fin the Cloghog Road area along with
OL,9,Fanother unidentified individual.
OL,11,FBritish troops who had been carrying
OL,12,Fout surveillance at the scene for
OL,13,Fthree days then opened fire on them,
OL,14,Faccording to the families' lawyers.
OL,16,FOne of the soldiers later told an
OL,17,Finquest that the IRA men had taken
OL,18,Fpossession of guns and were pointing
OL,19,Fthem in the direction of the military
OL,20,Funit.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778253065
OL,3,CFamilies of IRA men shot dead reach
OL,4,Csettlements in claims for damages
OL,6,FUp to 79 bullet cartridges recovered
OL,7,Ffrom the scene were said to be
OL,8,Ftraceable to the soldiers' weapons.
OL,10,FThe inquest, held in 1985, made no
OL,11,Fsignificant findings about the
OL,12,Fcircumstances surrounding the deaths.
OL,14,FBut an expert report commissioned as
OL,15,Fpart of an Historical Enquiries Team
OL,16,F(HET) probe in 2013 concluded that the
OL,17,Fpositioning of McGirr's body was
OL,18,Fconsistent with him kneeling when
OL,19,Fshot, lawyers said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
