OL,3,CFamilies of IRA men shot dead reach
OL,4,Csettlements in claims for damages
OL,6,FA further finding was made that no
OL,7,Fshots had struck Campbell from the
OL,8,Ffront.
OL,10,FBased on that report relatives of both
OL,11,Fmen issued legal proceedings for
OL,12,Fdamages against the MoD and PSNI in
OL,13,F2016.
OL,15,FTheir barrister, Des Fahy KC, told the
OL,16,Fcourt that undisclosed settlements
OL,17,Fhave now been reached in the claims.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
