OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778253065
OL,3,CFamilies of IRA men shot dead reach
OL,4,Csettlements in claims for damages
OL,6,FMr Justice Rooney responded: "It is
OL,7,Fgood news to hear that two actions
OL,8,Fhave been resolved after this length
OL,9,Fof time."
OL,11,FSpeaking outside court, the families'
OL,12,Fsolicitor, Padraig O Muirigh,
OL,13,Findicated the confidential terms were
OL,14,Fagreed following weeks of negotiations.
OL,16,F"I can confirm that my clients are
OL,17,Fsatisfied with the outcome of this
OL,18,Flitigation (and) will now be making a
OL,19,Fdonation to charity," he said.
OL,26,@nD@^OUqD@IO]xD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
