OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778253065
OL,3,CFamilies of IRA men shot dead reach
OL,4,Csettlements in claims for damages
OL,6,FMr O Muirigh claimed the families had
OL,7,Ffought for more than 40 years to
OL,8,Fexpose the circumstances surrounding
OL,9,Fthe deaths of their loved ones.
OL,11,F"They have always maintained that the
OL,12,FBritish Army operated a 'shoot to
OL,13,Fkill' policy during the conflict," he
OL,14,Fadded.
OL,16,F"The search of the arms dump appears
OL,17,Fto have been intelligence-led and the
OL,18,Ffamilies have always questioned why
OL,19,Fthe deceased were not apprehended at
OL,20,Fthe scene."
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@bO]xD@AOU|D@KO]
